cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Test Suite — the bench for real autodidaxis"
message: "If you use this test suite, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Gupta
    given-names: Dhruv
abstract: >-
  A test suite of ~43 publicly accessible datasets with naturally occurring
  out-of-distribution (OOD) shift, built as the evaluation bench for auto-didactic
  neuro-symbolic world models (part of world-model-lab). It measures whether a
  self-built theory of a domain survives natural distribution shift and matches a
  per-dataset rubric of established facts, testable hypotheses, expected
  intuitions, and genuine unknowns.
license: CC-BY-4.0
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-05-29"
url: "https://github.com/Zetetic-Dhruv/world-model-lab/tree/main/test-suite"
keywords:
  - autodidaxis
  - neuro-symbolic
  - world-models
  - out-of-distribution
  - distribution-shift
  - benchmark
